      "mitigation": "P126 dry-run must verify row-count delta matches exactly N_bets \u00d7 N_draws",
      "severity": "medium"
    },
    {
      "risk_id": "RSR-4",
      "description": "Adapter get_all_bets() not uniformly implemented",
